 * ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 * Session-level coaching limits for the LLM Coach.
 *
 * Rules:
 *   - Max 3 coaching injections per agent session
 *   - Sessions expire after 30 minutes of inactivity
 *   - Coaching retires automatically when a task_type has
